  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study was designed in order to investigate the effects of 3 different dialysate calcium
      concentrations may exert on mineral metabolism and hemodynamic stability in standard
      hemodialysis (hd).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
